Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:33.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:36.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you not know what your boyfriend's post graduation plans are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:39.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... We never talk about stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:40.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.09,0:01:43.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already a senior, but you haven't discussed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:45.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you normally talk about, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:51.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff like the upcoming Umibouzu concert...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:54.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Or guessing what order he'll perform his songs in...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:55.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it would be something like that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:01:56.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:02:01.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't your boyfriend's post graduation plans a source for concern when making your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:05.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you two talk about this stuff with Nakao-chi and Suzuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:06.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.24,0:02:10.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao-chi is going into the family business, running a dessert shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:13.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm planning to become a nutritionist to help him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:16.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Kazuyoshi Yamaguchi's wife, huh? How admirable!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.67,0:02:21.01,lovely - TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazutoyo Yamauchi is a Japanese historical figure from the Warring States period. His wife was known to be highly loyal to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.67,0:02:19.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! That's Kazutoyo Yamauchi's wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:21.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:22.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Chiharu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:26.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to go to the same university as Suzuki-kun for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:28.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:30.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:34.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...comparatively I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:39.36,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(984,0)\1c&HFFFFFF&\2c&H00FFFF&\pos(391,391)}{\fs26}Premonition of Separation?! Risa and Otani's Different Paths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:42.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to university.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:44.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! University?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:45.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to act so surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:47.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:48.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:49.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:51.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you really are serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:54.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you'll get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:56.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:58.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sitting entrance exams isn't free, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:02:59.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:05.68,lovely - TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Here "ronin" refers to a high school graduate who failed to get into university, and is studying to retake entrance exams the following year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:02.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you become a ronin, it'll cost you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:05.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Reconsider before you go wasting your time and money, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:09.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've at least said "Wow! Go for it!"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:10.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not cute at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:13.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. I am impressed by your reckless, adventurous spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:16.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not going to say "go for it".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:18.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you really feel, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:20.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Otani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:22.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were her, I'd be trying to stop you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:23.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:24.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I would indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:29.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you guys take me for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:31.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,An idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:32.27,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(670,-70,-260,280,[0,0])\frz20\fs60\bord1\1c&HD97E98&\3c&HA76A86&\fsp13}IDIOT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:36.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the only one you hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:38.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're the most annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:41.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sorry for being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:44.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all damn rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:46.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the type who can do anything if I put my mind to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:48.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably can't do it even if you put your mind to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:49.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:52.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to try, and I'm definitely going to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:55.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You just watch, you bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:02.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to laugh at me some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:06.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:10.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Otani, why do you want to go to college all of the sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:12.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not all of the sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:14.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:19.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's old man Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play basketball!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:23.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You gave me a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:25.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play! Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:32.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This old man has to study for exams. I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:34.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How uncool. Exams...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:37.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Now hurry up and get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:40.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:41.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:42.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids from my neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:45.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I play basketball with them from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:47.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean they play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:48.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:53.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway... I want to play basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:54.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,At university?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:56.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean after university.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:00.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,As a school basketball coach or something, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to university, getting certified,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:06.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,and playing basketball with brats like that everyday...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:08.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:11.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you want to get a teaching certificate? You want to become a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just giving you an example!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:16.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I do like kids and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:21.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Elementary kids and such...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,An elementary school teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:26.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,For example. Just for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:30.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani... a school teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:36.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Otani-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:38.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're laughing too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:44.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I didn't want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl... She's definitely the old man's girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:50.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But old man Otani's shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:51.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's what they call "{\i1}disparity{\i0}".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:53.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:56.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me that basketball. I'm confiscating it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Give it back, baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:06:00.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not bald bald! If you want it, come get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:05.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That Otani... He's a big hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:11.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So Otani wants to become an elementary teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:16.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If he does, it'd be hard to tell who's the kid and who's the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:20.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it's nice to see him smile like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:25.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Half of me thinks it's impossible, but I'll support him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:27.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:33.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But before I knew it, something happened that would have a deeper impact than Otani's college plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:38.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:40.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to an undergraduate university in Hokkaido?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.89,0:06:43.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You guys haven't heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:47.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:54.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan, what is this all of the sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:56.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you liked our trip there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:06:59.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:01.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Then why, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:03.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are your parents getting transfered?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:07.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma's body is deteriorating, so she's going to go and live in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going along to take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:11.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But... What about your mom and dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:14.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,They've both got jobs here, so they can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:17.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She says she has some old friends up there,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:19.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,but Grandma will get lonely all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:23.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with this, Nakao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:25.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A long distance relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:29.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem! It'll be fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:33.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll call everyday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:34.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:37.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan and Nakao-chi are going to maintain a long distance relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:40.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Risa, will you come shopping with me after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:43.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have to study for the entrance exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:45.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The undergraduate university in Hokkaido offers entry by referral.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:49.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,All I need to get in, is a high school diploma and an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:51.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:52.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. So I'm all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:55.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:57.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:00.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,For not telling you about going to Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:02.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. You only just decided, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:03.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:06.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, are you really planning on buying all of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:08.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I came shopping today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't come back just to shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:12.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:17.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,When I told Grandma I'd go with her to Hokkaido, she gave me quite a bit of spending money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:19.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:24.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Nobu-chan, your grandma has given you a lot of money over the years, hasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:27.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's why, in a sense, I'm doing this to repay her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:30.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I love my grandma, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Nakao-chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:40.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I love him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:45.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:48.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Nakao-chi is okay with it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:52.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming over to have dinner at my place tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:55.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Risa, which of these is better?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:56.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:01.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we are talking about the self-assured, strong-willed Nobu-chan, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:06.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where she goes, I'm sure she has the confidence to do well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:12.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao-chi, I'm going to get some eggs, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:13.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:15.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao-chi, is this really alright with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:23.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really alright if I take Nobuko so far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:26.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I care about you too, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:28.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be worried if you went all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:35.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to have such a wonderful granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And she has such a wonderful boyfriend too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:39.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:45.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:53.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Grandma's going to perform an act she's saved specially for Nakao-chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:53.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,An act?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:09:59.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:01.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:03.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Carp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:08.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He liked it! He liked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:13.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma, your body is weak. Don't over exert yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:17.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:19.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:23.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao-chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:26.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:27.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:31.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:33.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:38.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,At that point,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:43.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,neither we nor Nobu-chan knew how Nakao-chi felt deep down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:48.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,As the day of Nobu-chan's interview in Hokkaido approached,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:51.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao-chi was falling apart inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:06.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao's been acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:07.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:09.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:11.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? It's weird, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:14.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. There's just no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:17.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How can it be? How can it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:20.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Life really is just great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:25.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon. It's a pleasure to meet you. Indeed, indeed. Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:26.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:30.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:33.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyah! Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:35.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao! What the heck were you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:38.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a boy in the girl's bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:38.19,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's spilling everywhere, Nakao.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:45.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I think it's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:48.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:50.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:52.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,With Nobu-chan going to Hokkaido, Nakao-chi is probably-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:55.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad news! Nakao fell down the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:58.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiharu-chan, where's Nobu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:01.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Gori-sensei called her to the office just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:04.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go find Nobu-chan. You go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:05.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:09.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't know what to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:12.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Good thing I walked away with just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.64,0:12:16.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "{\i1}good thing{\i0}", you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:20.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:23.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you did, you wouldn't have fallen down the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:24.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:27.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:29.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been acting weird lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:34.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:38.21,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\1c&H4D3C1B&\fsp13\fnTimes New Roman\fs24\pos(363,89)}Infirmary
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:39.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want Nobu-chan to go to Hokkaido, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:41.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:48.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll make Nobu-chan feel bad, so I can't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:51.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, she's made her final decision and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:56.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:58.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:08.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:14.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:21.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa! What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:24.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it over for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:26.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave it so much thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:28.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:35.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:40.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you've always been the one to help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:44.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I don't have any advice I can give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:46.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:49.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I was expecting any advice from you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:52.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying that doesn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:55.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you chase after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:57.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did intend to say something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:01.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you're on about!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:04.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:06.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We should leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:07.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:10.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:12.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to say to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:14.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:21.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling "{\i1}Nakao-chi{\i0}"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:24.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with those glasses, Nakao-chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:27.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, stop adding the "{\i1}chi{\i0}" after Nakao.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:30.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfashionable and out of date these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:31.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:33.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao-chi's gone crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:35.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "{\i1}Master{\i0}".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:39.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:42.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go, then go by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with some other girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:46.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were going to settle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:50.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never told you this before, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:53.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...I've actually got three other women.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:55.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you knock it off already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:58.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you, Nakao-chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:01.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me? I said I've got three other women!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:04.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Nakao-chi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:06.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Maiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:14.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is lover #1, Maiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:17.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma-Mai-Mai-M-M-Maity?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:20.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Maiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:24.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing?! Get out of here! Get!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:26.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear. Even you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:27.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:34.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Su-Su-Su-Suzuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:35.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:38.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And lover #3, Haruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:40.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:42.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let Haruko make her appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:43.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:47.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Your make up isn't done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:49.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:52.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao-chi, What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:56.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just forget a terrible guy like me, Nobuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:01.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go live in a harem with these lovers of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a bather to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:05.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A bather?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:07.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,My gut tells me he meant "{\i1}bother{\i0}".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:09.09,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz5\fs32\fscy180\fnComic Sans MS\bord1\1c&H373B5E&\3c&H363745&\fsp5\pos(404,342)}BATHER
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:09.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bather...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:10.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:13.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:16.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Then get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:19.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:23.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Haruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:27.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:28.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:30.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan! Nobu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:36.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You there! You, man standing there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:39.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was that disgusting display for?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:43.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I want Nobu-chan to hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:48.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If she hates me and forgets about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:51.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,she can go to Hokkaido without any worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:54.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your help, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:57.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Why you didn't you tell me about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:00.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause you'd get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:01.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:10.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to cry about it, don't do things like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:14.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want her to leave, just tell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:16.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:28.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I know you went to a lot of trouble to get these,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:32.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,but Grandma would be upset if I poked holes in my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:36.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I thought you had ears pierced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:40.43,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz24\fs19\fscy180\fnComic Sans MS\bord0\1c&H818C78&\pos(395,230)}Message:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:40.43,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\fnComic Sans MS\bord5\1c&HF2FFFA&\3c&HC6D8CB&\frz27.022\pos(333,258)}{\bord8.75}Risa
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:50.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still going to Hokkaido after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:52.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:57.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It might have seen silly, but that little display really got to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:18:00.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,After having that done for my benefit, I don't really have much choice but to go, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:03.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... You know, Nobu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:09.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to you that I was able to get together with Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:11.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, all of the sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:16.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to keep trying so hard because you were around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:20.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd been on my own, I'd probably just have done weird thing up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:24.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.Policeman! There's a suspicious person over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:25.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:26.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:33.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if you've thought it over and decided, it can't be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:36.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Things should work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:38.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Things will definitely work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:42.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to the decision to go to Hokkaido yourself, so it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:49.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine so... believe in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:51.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:54.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I can't say anything more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:56.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No. This is plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:19:00.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:02.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:08.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Risa, I have a favor to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:15.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as Nobu-chan has always had my back, it's my turn to help her this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:17.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm coming straight back after my interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:22.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:24.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,In spring you won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:26.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's months from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:30.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao didn't come? I did call him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:34.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I'm only going for the interview this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:35.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:43.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao-chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:44.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:48.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:50.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:56.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:58.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:04.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember these?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:08.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,They were the first present I ever gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:12.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You got your ears pierced?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:16.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Risa to take me get them done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But won't your grandma get mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:23.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be alright. But I won't be able to wear them until they heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:25.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I get there, I'll wear these every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:28.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, I won't ever forget you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:31.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:39.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:41.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you more than anything in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:45.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:48.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-What are they saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:52.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is much more embarrassing than a simple "{\i1}don't go{\i0}".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:54.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So what? They're happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:56.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:01.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan got her happy ending,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:04.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,but what's going to happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:10.77,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs10\bord0\1c&000000&\pos(589,362)}Fortunes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:11.89,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs10\bord0\1c&000000&\1a&FF&\pos(589,362)}Fortunes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:12.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:15.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:19.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to have some woman trouble soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:21.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what this baby here just told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:24.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:26.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:28.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,One is a woman much older then you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:32.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The other is a woman over 170 cm tall,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:34.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Only slightly older then you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:38.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right about the older woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:41.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't know anybody that tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:43.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I've got to get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:46.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! The fortune telling fee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:50.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. And my powers were working properly for once too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:57.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This short boy would end up having an even deeper impact on us than Nobu-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:00.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,although we didn't know it at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:27.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Kozmui is cheating on me with a short guy from work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.70,0:23:28.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:30.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would date a guy that short if they had a choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:31.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making fun of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.92,0:23:32.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.74,0:23:34.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovely Complex~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:37.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Next: Otani's Catastrophic Declaration!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.70,0:23:39.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\pos(358,305)}Otani's Catastrophic Declaration!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:37.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to watch!
